            hello@deadhangs.com
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-card">
          <h3>Content Corrections</h3>
          <p>Spotted an error in our data or training guidance? We take accuracy seriously and will update content promptly.</p>
          <a href="mailto:hello@deadhangs.com?subject=Content+Correction" class="email-link">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M3 4a1 1 0 00-1 1v10a1 1 0 001 1h14a1 1 0 001-1V5a1 1 0 00-1-1H3zm0 2.586l7 4.667 7-4.667V15H3V6.586z"/></svg>
            hello@deadhangs.com
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-form">
        <h2>Send a Message</h2>
        <p>We aim to respond within 2 business days. Please be specific â€” training questions get the best answers with your current hold time, age, and training history.</p>

        <form id="contact-form" action="https://api.staticforms.xyz/submit" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="accessKey" value="sf_9e906eb6c00416b9d3354749">
          <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="DeadHangs.com Contact Form">
          <input type="hidden" name="replyTo" value="@">
          <input type="hidden" name="redirectTo" value="https://deadhangs.com/contact/?sent=1">

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Your Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="e.g. Alex" required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="email">Email Address</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="subject-select">Topic</label>
            <select id="subject-select" name="$subject">
